South African Contract Cleaners to Start Pay Strike on Aug. 8, Union Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-04T06:36:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-04/south-african-contract-cleaners-to-start-pay-strike-on-aug-8-union-says.html
As many as 100,000 contract cleaning
workers in  South Africa  will start a strike over pay on Aug. 8,
the South African Transport & Allied Workers’ Union said.  “We intend to put pressure on cleaning sector employers to
return to the negotiating table and offer working conditions and
salaries which will improve conditions in this most vulnerable
sector,” the labor union said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  